Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:22.90,zero-op(cn),NTP,0,0,0,,为了创造无泣世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:29.41,zero-op(cn),NTP,0,0,0,,赤色浸染天空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:35.72,zero-op(cn),NTP,0,0,0,,呐喊祈祷随风而逝
