Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:57.52,zero-op(cn),NTP,0,0,0,,面对彼方渐闭双瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:03.08,zero-op(cn),NTP,0,0,0,,双手仍旧伸向远方
